dct_description_sm: by Johvan Loon Plaetsnyder en Zee-kaert-maker, en Joh: Janssonius van Waesberge.
3 bar scales on map, given in “Duytsche mylen,” “Spaensche mylen,” “Engels. en Fran. mylen.”
Decorative cartouches, compass rose, rhumb lines, cherubs.
Appears in van Loon’s Klaer lichtende noort-ster, ofte, Zee atlas: waer in vertoont de gelegentheydt van alle de zee-kusten des geheelen aerdtbodems, Amsterdam, 1661.
